  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a clay tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the collard greens, lemon juice, chickpeas, and chopped preserved lemon, and stir to combine.",
    "Cover the tagine and transfer it to a bain-marie, and cook for 30 minutes over low heat.",
    "Remove the tagine from the bain-marie and stir in the chopped parsley.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
